es cognitifs qui nuisent à l’évolution du droit criminel et à l’émergence d’idées innovantes susceptibles de soutenir et de motiver des pratiques alternatives.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aCriminal justice, Administration of. 0aCriminal lawxPhilosophy. 0aDroit pénalxPhilosophie. 0aJustice pénalexAdministration. 0aPeines. 0aPunishment. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Criminology.2bisacsh1 aAssis Machado, Marta Rodriguez de, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCauchie, Jean-François, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDubé, Richard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDubé, Richard, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aGarcia, Margarida, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGarcia, Margarida, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHerrera-Vega, Eliana, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLachambre, Sébastien, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLehalle, Sandra, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMachado, Maíra Rocha, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPires, Alvaro P., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPiñero, Veronica, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPossas, Mariana T., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRaupp, Mariana, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRocha Machado, Maíra, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aTulkens, Françoise, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aXavier, José Roberto, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.